                <h1>Discover the Fascinating Disney Timeline: From Mickey to Marvel</h1>
                <p>Disney's timeline illustrates the evolution of a global entertainment giant. Starting with the creation of Mickey Mouse in 1928, Disney expanded into theme parks with Disneyland in 1955 and ventured into animated classics like "The Lion King" in 1994. The acquisition of Pixar, Marvel, and Lucasfilm solidified its status in modern filmmaking.</p>
